      "Path:     /var/run/nscd/dbSz9CTr\n"
      "Mode:     r\n"
      "Severity: 3\n"
      "\n"
      "  1 - /var/run/nscd/dbSz9CTr\n"
      " [2 - /var/run/nscd/*]\n"
      "\n"
      "(A)llow / [(D)eny] / (G)lob / Glob w/(E)xt / (N)ew / Abo(r)t / (F)inish / (O)pts\n"
      "Adding /var/run/nscd/* r to profile.\n"
      "\n"
      "Profile:  /usr/sbin/httpd2-prefork\n"
