#. Tag: para
#: apparmor_profiles_man.xml:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Like the graphical front-end for building &aa; profiles, the &yast; Add Profile Wizard, <command>aa-genprof</command> also supports the use of the local profile repository under <filename>/etc/apparmor/profiles/extras</filename> <!-- path will change in &aa; ;-) 3.0 --> and the remote &aa; profile repository."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: apparmor_profiles_man.xml:1305
#, no-c-format
